column5: And they are all idiots anyway,so it seems

If u have ever been prescribed antidepressants, effexor is a strong one.There is no comparison between your self medicating choices (weed,done) and effexor.naturally a psych would prescribe what he knows about,but anti depressants only work in30% of people. Effexor is foul and a psychotic freak out.in my experience. The psych will tell u it takes a few weeks to work.maybe its right for you but u will suffer before that happens, if it does.Just forget meds or use what u know works for you.good luck.
You will be very sick and you will look for relief.possible ,but not worth it if u have a choice.wont hurt you in the long term tho.
